dc_title_s: Local Public Health Department Office Boundaries, Wisconsin 2022
dc_description_s: This data represents local public health department office boundaries for Wisconsin in 2022. [This dataset contains the boundaries of local health department offices in Wisconsin. Wisconsin local health departments play a central role in providing essential public health services in communities. For more information please visit the Wisconsin Department of Health Services website: https://www.dhs.wisconsin.gov/lh-depts/counties.htm]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data.dhsgis.wi.gov/datasets/wi-dhs::wisconsin-local-public-health-department-office-boundaries/about
